<main class="container-fluid bg-white position-relative">
  <%= image_tag("workout/1.jpg", width:"100%") %>

  <div class="container-fluid resize position-absolute text-center">
    <div class="container-fluid fadeIn" style="background: rgba(192,192,192,0.4); color:#ffffff; font-size: 5vmin; font-weight: bold; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px">
      <p>Your personal manager</p>
      <p>leading your body perfect</p>
    </div>
    <%= link_to "Register Now!", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-outline-warning btn-lg"%>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center col-md-10 mx-auto" style="padding:40px">
    <h1 class="p-2">About</h1>
    <div class="row m-5">
      <div class="col-12", id="about">
        <p>
          A tool that better manages training results.
          Records remain in a visible form, so you can check your growth while maintaining your personal motivation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="p-2">Feature</h1>
    <div class="row justify-content-around align-items-center m-5">
      <div class="col-6 sbox position-relative">
        <%= image_tag "home/calendar.png", width:"70%", class:"position-absolute", style:"top: 0; left: 0;"  %>
        <%= image_tag "home/record.png", width:"70%", class:"position-absolute", style:"top: 25%; left: 25%;" %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6">
        <p>
          You can record your daily workouts and manage them in chronological order.
          Since vol is automatically calculated when a record is registered, it can be tracked more smoothly than ever even if the number of times or weight changes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row justify-content-around align-items-center m-5">
      <div class="col-6">
        <p>
          The registered exercises can be analyzed on the Chart page for one month.
          As for the frequency of exercise, you can check the change in vol, the ratio of exercise performed, etc.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6">
        <%= image_tag "home/feed.png", width:"100%" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row justify-content-around align-items-center m-5">
      <div class="col-6">
        <%= image_tag "home/chart.png", width:"100%" %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6">
        <p>
          You can also see the activity of other users you have designated to follow and share your progress with your friends.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</main>

<script>
  $(function() {
    $('.fadeIn').addClass('show');
    width = ($(window).width())/5 - 70;
    $('.resize').css("top", width + "px");
  });
</script>